永遠都找少，屌佢老母"},{"pid":"1d8794a7f85a6032bdb24a3f1c812c6654cafa41","tid":348342,"uid":17351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔用電子貨幣係因為DC9 要避稅<br />\n<br />\n毫子位0捨9進都算，起碼叫肯載你<br />\n平時有d 仆街到<span style=\"color: red;\">鎖埋門拒載</span><br />\n又話者咩九龍車唔過海<br />\n<br />\n屌 跟本政府打擊DC9 不力<br />\n刑罰又無阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n應該要加dc9 扣分制<br />\n投訴dc9 成立 按 嚴重性扣分<br />\n扣夠某個分數停牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n司機怎可以說不載？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aca5f6b5c25bf54f0d5f67b322084fc8038c9db","tid":348342,"uid":25349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔用電子貨幣係因為DC9 要避稅<br />\n<br />\n毫子位0捨9進都算，起碼叫肯載你<br />\n平時有d 仆街到鎖埋門拒載<br />\n又話者咩九龍車唔過海<br />\n<br />\n屌 跟本政府打擊DC9 不力<br />\n刑罰又無阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n應該要加dc9 扣分制<br />\n投訴dc9 成立 按 嚴重性扣分<br />\n扣夠某個分數停牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班的士狗仲會自己造數呃埋政府果個鼓勵就業交通津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前做pt 曾經申請過，跟我file 果勞工署職員會打電話黎問一問你資料，吹開水佢講好多的士狗個個月走黎申請，自己造到條數唔過入息上限，佢都話揸的士人工邊有可能咁低，但的士狗又提供到證明，結果都係吹佢唔脹要批比佢，果陣個職員都話班友好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b76bd0618abd6dc7ce82ce4e51fbe55184c230","tid":348342,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"架車都唔好坐既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7369715029b4b3c1807c177b90fdc7d30b470efd","tid":348342,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:35:07.000Z","msg":"八達通比錢都好啦. <br />\n不過的士佬都費事比手續費."},{"pid":"3ff23f2498d5592cefe13510644ede829a1ffe04","tid":348342,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"因為政府要保住現有持份者利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62907ca66b2fe52dddc3c0022065c59732114fd4","tid":348342,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"有競爭咩？"},{"pid":"0903b15cf6df01eb7cab0304e23d3325478042cb","tid":348342,"uid":19923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"次次我都自己4捨5入俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 30.4就一定俾30，47.7就俾48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢夠膽出聲屌我俾少佢我一定屌鳩佢即刻俾1000蚊佢找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c40d6392c33317295cdc9eba06eb869ef17abbe","tid":348342,"uid":66253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be7566d5e48da6cf295862d6c53da5e03e8231d4","tid":348342,"uid":3032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:06:21.000Z","msg":"應該推行電子貨幣<br />\nEg支付寶"},{"pid":"6a8094c57e1c20285cd3dba2acfa0770f0129edb","tid":348342,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該推行電子貨幣<br />\nEg支付寶</blockquote><br />\n的士佬認為既問題都係起度。<br />\n手續費。報稅。如果有折扣又點攪<br />\nuber方法好D"},{"pid":"99bd7bdb7598153bbbb244ec7ecf6821f3900a70","tid":348342,"uid":54279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔用電子貨幣係因為DC9 要避稅<br />\n<br />\n毫子位0捨9進都算，起碼叫肯載你<br />\n平時有d 仆街到鎖埋門拒載<br />\n又話者咩九龍車唔過海<br />\n<br />\n屌 跟本政府打擊DC9 不力<br />\n刑罰又無阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n應該要加dc9 扣分制<br />\n投訴dc9 成立 按 嚴重性扣分<br />\n扣夠某個分數停牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關事<br />\n八達通既話就係<br />\n但如果用個人account mobile payment第一稅局冇權查<br />\n第二純個人P2P過數大把理由解釋，佢prove唔到你係的士收入</blockquote><br />\n稅局好大權架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地真係有權問銀行攞客戶既交易紀錄<br />\n至於p2p過數，你話你間中一次半次都可能解到，如果你一日之內同好多人p2p, 你估稅局傻架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd28075c9ef55ddd26b8cd6202cbc23dd99ad00e","tid":348342,"uid":2692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次我都自己4捨5入俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 30.4就一定俾30，47.7就俾48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢夠膽出聲屌我俾少佢我一定屌鳩佢即刻俾1000蚊佢找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係撐的士佬，不過好似寫到明500，1000大紙冇得找係唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過自己搭開，的士佬一兩毫子多數唔收，其餘自動加到整數黎收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae71f2e9bdafdde2f561df2fd5b87a24487e0253","tid":348342,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔用電子貨幣係因為DC9 要避稅<br />\n<br />\n毫子位0捨9進都算，起碼叫肯載你<br />\n平時有d 仆街到鎖埋門拒載<br />\n又話者咩九龍車唔過海<br />\n<br />\n屌 跟本政府打擊DC9 不力<br />\n刑罰又無阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n應該要加dc9 扣分制<br />\n投訴dc9 成立 按 嚴重性扣分<br />\n扣夠某個分數停牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nuber佬有分數制度但佢地都成日拒載人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f12536daed947ea66af52389b8015b4efb5f729","tid":348342,"uid":4758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:45:00.000Z","msg":"講到底都係因為的士牌喺香港係當做資產而唔係經營權"},{"pid":"62331a39de6b8dbb5ed923923a4583b754446138","tid":348342,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔用電子貨幣係因為DC9 要避稅<br />\n<br />\n毫子位0捨9進都算，起碼叫肯載你<br />\n平時有d 仆街到鎖埋門拒載<br />\n又話者咩九龍車唔過海<br />\n<br />\n屌 跟本政府打擊DC9 不力<br />\n刑罰又無阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n應該要加dc9 扣分制<br />\n投訴dc9 成立 按 嚴重性扣分<br />\n扣夠某個分數停牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本唔應該比佢分過唔過海<br />\n所有車去邊都要接<br />\n一拒絕（乜春交更唔過海嗰啲）即刻報警"},{"pid":"76c7cf0f5480366d6f94d4eda3fd1c7c8251c22a","tid":348342,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失敗計劃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/160609_6d1ee73bf881e056d9ba737f995b5907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F160609_6d1ee73bf881e056d9ba737f995b5907.jpg&h=3badb368&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/160610_960569d3e4c133974ee62ddc6d5c3233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F160610_960569d3e4c133974ee62ddc6d5c3233.jpg&h=3d877276&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢舊野把聲好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且要搵目的地要打上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd85d5ff11a18c6c729eefc13b3b99ae40a03c4","tid":348342,"uid":2582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:51:03.000Z","msg":"Gps都冇已經狗都唔屌<br />\n去親邊度都唔識路"},{"pid":"081b4f3d031c7c1c5140315f73b475f8db94e2e9","tid":348342,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:53:24.000Z","msg":"司機自己可唔可以整個信用卡機，八達通機收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39002052972c3bb19460991ec64bc31a16ad5d88","tid":348342,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"的士佬好多住公屋<br />\n<br />\n一家三口，佢努力d搵兩萬幾一個月，報一萬都得"},{"pid":"7e232b30e58215a448a8daf6fc6b49e1b08bf74e","tid":348342,"uid":103031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0