itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"避稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a30e47e784cee3c7f1bc4c69a2a8d714552a8b9","tid":348342,"uid":37566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌佢老母的士佬<br />\n<br />\n成鳩日30.4 &gt; 31<br />\n<br />\n跟住有次47.7我俾47然後烚熟</blockquote><br />\n31蚊俾100找我60都試過<br />\n屌佢老母嗰時趕時間落咗車行咗幾步先發現<br />\n車牌睇唔切，嗰時返學就遲到冇追車<br />\n屌佢老母次次諗起都嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8950efc894b990f31218e09f28295745a00ff00e","tid":348342,"uid":131423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:37:08.000Z","msg":"當好多地方都用到apple pay、visa paywave<br />\n連隧道都就講用到八達通<br />\n的士仲係現金<br />\n美帝的士都收信用卡啦<br />\n國際大都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33c866b3e55de38955b7a03f2d4571a208f6e01","tid":348342,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:39:31.000Z","msg":"最撚好笑係而家推埋啲優質的士牌<br />\n原因係的士唔夠優質， 屌你唔識叫的士狗做好啲㗎？？ 做唔好咪唔比佢揸囉<br />\n的士就的士， 又要分優唔優質， 咁小巴巴士做得唔好又洗唔洗整個優質小巴牌？<br />\n咁如果他日優質的士又做得唔好又如何？<br />\n係咪停佢牌？ 唔比佢揸？<br />\n如果係咁點解呢條規例唔喺而家的士狗度實施改善質素？ 所以政府諗嘢真係好好笑<br />\n根本成班利益輸送"},{"pid":"67c715439fc5909480571c1aa945114cfdf5dd9b","tid":348342,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"用電子貨幣咪要明碼實價？啲司機點呃錢"},{"pid":"07da5aae89088b72b8d2c7ed6213af44555efa59","tid":348342,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當好多地方都用到apple pay、visa paywave<br />\n連隧道都就講用到八達通<br />\n的士仲係現金<br />\n美帝的士都收信用卡啦<br />\n國際大都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n的士狗唔會咁諗"},{"pid":"5e11dcda98941395f942e0a4e9fc7235ace1bff1","tid":348342,"uid":4360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有啲的士佬唔識路都係問題<br />\n連down個app都唔識係度賴少行果頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次搭的士佢唔識路要我開住google map 教佢行</blockquote><br />\n我都試過 要搵埋咩交界比佢 就到個陣要同佢講轉左轉右 都唔知邊個先係司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢問你路係想知你對條路有冇認識<br />\n如果你唔識就兜硬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次我唔係好舒服，佢問我點行我話你決定啦唔塞 最快就得<br />\n佢帶我喺我屋企附近兜咗10分鐘<br />\n之後忍唔撚住問佢 你由70蚊開始兜到而家，肯車我返屋企未，一係直接去差館（屋企附近有差館）<br />\n<br />\n之後佢死死氣車我返去，話收我70算啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536aa50eb46de8b8823c0d40bb42abc07e09ce6b","tid":348342,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當好多地方都用到apple pay、visa paywave<br />\n連隧道都就講用到八達通<br />\n的士仲係現金<br />\n美帝的士都收信用卡啦<br />\n國際大都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n的士狗唔會咁諗</blockquote><br />\n而家有1間車行肯裝卡機<br />\n1間囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他繼續現金玩上捨入屈多幾毫子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6265f1f6aeaa1edd9bdd7283c798da0525733f","tid":348342,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"現金交易唔使報稅，又可以話收入不足申請公屋"},{"pid":"2916b55bb193ab179378faaf31cd7e9e0fa53007","tid":348342,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"的士咁都仲未比人淘汰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988d2c318a7ce6c4d3e9207ba93f350d1357ddee","tid":348342,"uid":39692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:17:27.000Z","msg":"試過夜晚搭30蚊 俾100蚊之後找兩張廿蚊 個陣以為一張係50 一張係20<br />\n正常落車個陣司機係咪會開燈 個次佢就係無開黑媽媽睇唔清楚就落咗車"},{"pid":"6dc85d91c31ea3a666a975769ec87c2e9b5b4757","tid":348342,"uid":4166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"用得電子貨幣咪姐係有紀錄囉，咁d司機點逃稅點拎公屋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105b142fcbc92799bb95188c6342d281e2b68490","tid":348342,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"依家起俄羅斯(聖彼得堡)搭的士比信用卡，人地係拎舊身份證size嘅野插落電話個headphone jack再比你插卡比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇翻香港啲的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9816734d4b4787fd4706863298e2c697ad8947d","tid":348342,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔用電子貨幣係因為DC9 要避稅<br />\n<br />\n毫子位0捨9進都算，起碼叫肯載你<br />\n平時有d 仆街到鎖埋門拒載<br />\n又話者咩九龍車唔過海<br />\n<br />\n屌 跟本政府打擊DC9 不力<br />\n刑罰又無阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n應該要加dc9 扣分制<br />\n投訴dc9 成立 按 嚴重性扣分<br />\n扣夠某個分數停牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔過海原因係一個的士牌兩個地方用"},{"pid":"75bddf43e856eb14bc44795c850787688c4a3ec5","tid":348342,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚好笑係而家推埋啲優質的士牌<br />\n原因係的士唔夠優質， 屌你唔識叫的士狗做好啲㗎？？ 做唔好咪唔比佢揸囉<br />\n的士就的士， 又要分優唔優質， 咁小巴巴士做得唔好又洗唔洗整個優質小巴牌？<br />\n咁如果他日優質的士又做得唔好又如何？<br />\n係咪停佢牌？ 唔比佢揸？<br />\n如果係咁點解呢條規例唔喺而家的士狗度實施改善質素？ 所以政府諗嘢真係好好笑<br />\n根本成班利益輸送</blockquote><br />\n應該我地返工都要整個優質員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工雙計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}